34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/feeling-lonely-your-car-centric-town-might-be-why-1849458430\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/feeling-lonely-your-car-centric-town-might-be-why-1849458430\"\u003eThere are some downsides to that plan\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, though, and we’re not just talking about the risk of \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/portland-demands-something-be-done-after-car-crashes-in-1851729435\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/portland-demands-something-be-done-after-car-crashes-in-1851729435\"\u003esomeone crashing their car into your house\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S2214367X24002175?via%3Dihub\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S2214367X24002175?via%3Dihub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eA new study found\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e that while not having a car in the U.S. is bad for your overall life satisfaction, so is being forced to drive more than half the time you leave the house, \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2024/dec/29/extreme-car-dependency-unhappiness-americans\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2024/dec/29/extreme-car-dependency-unhappiness-americans\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003ethe \u003cem\u003eGuardian \u003c/em\u003ereports\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Basically, having to drive all the time is making you less happy. - Collin Woodard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embed